=== Czech ===

There is a package [https://github.com/hydandata/czech-holidays czech-holidays] which is available through ##MELPA##. Add following call somewhere in your init file. Note that this must be called before Emacs calendar is loaded.
    
    (czech-holidays-add)

If you have ##org-agenda-include-diary## set to ##t##, these will be also listed in the ##org-agenda## view.

=== Korean ===

There is a package, cal-korea-x that support Korean lunar calendar, and display names for months.  See [http://github.com/cinsk/cal-korea-x/ cal-korea-x].

